@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cpvusv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = ((v2 * v0) / tmp)
    v1 = tmp
    v2 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.87 - v2 + 0.51) - wp.abs(v0 + 0.43)))
    tmp = (v2 * 0.76)
    v0 = (v2 + wp.exp(v2))
    v0 = (wp.sin(tmp) - (wp.exp(v0 + 0.18) + (v1 + 0.38 - tmp + 0.13)))
    data[tid] = v0
